Source: gnomesword
Build-Depends: autotools-dev, quilt, patchutils (>= 0.2.25), cdbs (>= 0.4.27-1), debhelper (>= 4.1.0), debhelper (>= 4.2.21), libsword-dev (>=1.5.10), gnome-spell, libgtkhtml3.8-dev, scrollkeeper, gnome-core-devel, gtkhtml3.8
Build-Conflicts: libgtkhtml3.2-dev, libgtkhtml3.6-dev
Section: gnome
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Gnomesword Developer Team <gnomesword-developers@lists.sourceforge.net>
Standards-Version: 3.6.2.0

Package: gnomesword
Architecture: any
Section: gnome
Provides: sword-frontend
Depends: firefox, gtkhtml3.8, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Bible study with GNOME
 A bible study program for GNOME using the SWORD library.
 Features:
  Search Bible and Commentary
  Search Personal notes
  Add personal notes to verses
  Bookmarks
  Parallel Page - Display up to five versions
  StudyPad for keeping notes
  Spellcheck for StudyPad and Personal notes (uses gnome-spell)
  Uses modules from the SWORD Project
  Support for Sword Bible, Commentary, Lexicon and General Book modules
